Interface BigNoteSequence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<NoteMeta>, java.io.Externalizable, java.lang.Iterable<NoteMeta>, java.util.List<NoteMeta>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface BigNoteSequence
extends java.io.Externalizable, java.util.List<NoteMeta>
    Author:
    Nathan T. Freeman The purpose of a BigNoteSequence is to represent Note references across multiple databases or even multiple servers. Unlike DocumentCollections or NoteCollections, NoteSequences are always ordered
